File: Former president Jacob Zuma (L) talks to President Cyril Ramaphosa. JOHANNESBURG - President Cyril Ramphosa says the ANC top brass will be engaging with former president Jacob Zuma. This is over his failure to appear at the State Capture Inquiry. WATCH: A real prospect of jail time for Jacob Zuma Ramaphosa says the message to Zuma will be clear, that all of us have to abide by the constitution and respect the judiciary.